Relative hypoglycemia in critically ill patients (MIMIC-III)

## [1] 0

Figure 1. CONSORT diagram

# Set margins and multiplot
par(mfrow = c(1, 1))
par(mar = c(0, 0, 0, 0))

# Initialise a plot device
openplotmat()

# Set the position of the boxes
# 1st column indicates x axis position between 0 and 1
# 2nd column indicates y axis position between 0 and 1
# automatically assigns vertical position
num_of_boxes <- 6
auto_coords = coordinates(num_of_boxes)
vert_pos = rev(auto_coords[,1])
box_pos <- matrix(nrow = num_of_boxes, ncol = 2, data = 0)
box_pos[1,] = c(0.20, vert_pos[1]) # 1st box
for (i in 2:(num_of_boxes-1)) {
  box_pos[i,] = c(0.70, vert_pos[i]) # 2nd-... box
}
box_pos[num_of_boxes,] = c(0.20, vert_pos[num_of_boxes])

# Add the box content
box_content <- matrix(nrow = num_of_boxes, ncol = 1, data = 0)
box_content[1] = paste("All hospital admissions in MIMIC-III \n n =", 
                       n_total_hosp_in_mimic) # 1st box
box_content[2] = paste("Exclude patients aged < 18 on hospital admission \n n =", 
                       n_total_hosp_in_mimic - n_exclude_children) # 2nd box
box_content[3] = paste("Exclude hospital admissions after 1st stay \n n =",
                       n_exclude_children - n_include_first_icustay_only)
box_content[4] = paste("Exclude admissions with < 2 glucose values within 6 hours \n n =",
                       n_include_first_icustay_only - n_exclude_lt2_glucose_values)
box_content[5] = paste("Exclude hospital admissions with hypoglycemia \n n =",
                       n_exclude_lt2_glucose_values - n_exclude_hypogycemic_admissions)
box_content[num_of_boxes] = paste("Study cohort \n n =",
                       n_final_study_group)

# Adjust the size of boxes to fit content
box_x <- c(0.20, rep(0.40, num_of_boxes-2), 0.20)
box_y <- rep(0.08, num_of_boxes)

# Draw the arrows
for (i in 2:(num_of_boxes-1)) {
  straightarrow(from = c(box_pos[1,1],box_pos[i,2]), to = box_pos[i,], lwd = 1)  
}
straightarrow(from = box_pos[1,], to = box_pos[num_of_boxes,], lwd = 1)

# Draw the boxes
for (i in 1:num_of_boxes) {
  textrect(mid = box_pos[i,], radx = box_x[i], rady = box_y[i], 
           lab = box_content[i], 
           shadow.col = "grey")
}
